Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Tetua sekalian, mari kita buat dunia menjadi lebih baik bersama-sama.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Saturn, Anda kenapa?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Ada apa ini?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Tim medis, segera datang ke sini!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Gawat sekali!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Pemegang kekuasaan tertinggi dunia tidak boleh sampai celaka!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Apakah ini sejenis penyakit?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Apa yang Anda butuhkan, Saturn?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Tidak disangka, aku ternyata...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Yang Mulia Imu!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Im...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Saturn, mengapa kau membiarkan Joy Boy melarikan diri?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Mu...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Mohon ampuni aku...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Tidak disangka kekuatan itu ternyata begitu sulit untuk dikendalikan...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Yang Mulia Im...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Sa... Saturn.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Ja... jadi tulang?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Lapisan Penelitian tidak berhasil direbut, ya?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Telah dihalangi oleh York.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Sialan!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Ke mana pun kita pergi, gelombang pikiran tetap akan sampai.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}York juga mungkin akan terhubung ke sini.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Aku tahu.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Itu juga masih lebih baik daripada menyerahkan barang aslinya.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Sebelum umat manusia bisa menggunakan otak genius ini dengan baik,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}biarlah kita yang mengelolanya.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Itu bisa memakan waktu hingga 500 tahun.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Apakah kau sudah mengatur Awan Pulau-nya menjadi tipe terapung?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Tentu saja.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Bagi orang-orang di dunia, Vegapunk sudah mati.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Jadi tidak bisa berkeliling dunia sesuka hati.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Tidak ada dana maupun material,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}maka tidak bisa membuat penemuan baru.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Kalau itu, kita harus mengandalkan teman.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Baiklah.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Bagaimana menurutmu?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Bukankah ini terlalu aneh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Apakah kau iri dengan tinggi badanku?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Jangan konyol!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Buang saja bagian tubuh milik York itu.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Benar juga, kesannya tidak bagus.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Halo, apakah ini Weatheria?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Aku adalah Vegapunk.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Ada urusan apa, bukankah kau sudah mati?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Apa yang akan terjadi?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Apakah aku akan mati?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Aku tidak ingin mati!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Aku ingin bertahan hidup dengan berenang!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Dengan kata lain,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}di dalam "Void Century" yang tidak diketahui oleh siapa pun,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}telah terjadi sebuah peperangan yang sangat besar.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Saat itu ada seseorang yang menggunakan Senjata Kuno{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}dan membuat dunia ini tenggelam ke laut sedalam 200 meter.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Selanjutnya, orang yang berhasil mendapatkan Rahasia Besar One Piece,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}dan menjadi Raja Bajak Laut,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}maka dia yang akan bisa mendapatkan kekuatan itu sekali lagi.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Kita tidak boleh hanya diam menunggu ajal saja.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Dunia yang tenggelam ke dalam laut, ya?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Jadi alasan Tenryuubito tinggal di Red Line yang merupakan tempat tertinggi di dunia juga adalah...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Tequila Wolf.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}[Tequila Wolf\NVodka Wolf]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Vodka Wolf.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}[Tequila Wolf\NVodka Wolf\NRum Wolf]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Rum Wolf.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}[Tequila Wolf\NVodka Wolf\NRum Wolf\NBourbon Wolf]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Bourbon Wolf.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Bangunan raksasa yang dibangun dengan memperbudak orang-orang sejak 700 tahun yang lalu juga adalah?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Benar sekali.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Benar, sekarang semuanya masuk akal.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Kau telah mendahuluiku!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Menyebalkan sekali!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Vegapunk, orang-orang yang memercayai kata-kata yang kau ucapkan dengan mempertaruhkan nyawa itu,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}belum tentu semuanya akan melakukan "persiapan" secara damai.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Jangan sampai kehilangan tujuan, Dragon.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Harus segera diselesaikan.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Jika tidak...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Dunia ini akan berubah menjadi tempat di mana orang-orang memperebutkan "zona aman".{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Sudah bangun!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Aku sedang berada di...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Syukurlah!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Kau tidak apa-apa, Lilith?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Lilith!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Syukurlah kau sudah sadar!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Tadi aku benar-benar merasa khawatir!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Sanji, kau berulah lagi.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Lilith.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Di sini adalah sebuah ruangan di atas kapal Suku Raksasa.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Segala sesuatunya berukuran sangat besar.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Suku Raksasa?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Lilith, sebenarnya...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Walaupun ini sangat sulit untuk dikatakan,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}selain dirimu, para Vegapunk yang lain{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}tidak ada satu pun yang berhasil kami bawa keluar.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Kami mohon maaf sebesar-besarnya.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Atlas menyerangmu{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}mungkin itu karena...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Tidak apa-apa, aku sudah tahu, aku baru saja mendengar semuanya.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Baru saja mendengar? Mendengar dari siapa?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Biarkan aku menangis sebentar.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Sebenarnya bagian mana dari dirimu yang dianggap jahat?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Aku lapar!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Perubahan suasana hatinya cepat sekali{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Begitu ya, jika kau punya nafsu makan{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Suku Raksasa sudah menyiapkan buah-buahan di atas meja.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Datanglah kemari setelah kau sudah tenang.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Aku pergi ke sana duluan.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Tapi, kenapa bisa merasa selapar ini, ya?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Ah, apakah karena otakku sudah terputus hubungannya dengan York?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Syukurlah Lilith sudah bangun, ya.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Apakah makanannya ada di atas sini?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Makanan?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Ah, meja makan.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Sekarang suasana di atas sana sangat suram.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Kenapa begitu?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Sialan, padahal kita sudah berjanji.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Apakah baik-baik saja?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Lilith, Luffy juga mengalami luka yang parah.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Dia terlalu murung dan tidak punya nafsu makan.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Padahal sudah berjanji akan menyelamatkan si Paman Apel.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Paman!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Dia hanya makan lima tangkai anggur.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Itu sudah cukup banyak, 'kan?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Begitukah? Dia merasa depresi karena hal itu?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Namun, tidak apa-apa.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Aku juga baru saja mendengarnya.{\b0}
